{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Primary Writing Tool:} Claude (Anthropic) {\b Manuscript Format:} Markdown {\b Version Control:} Git/GitHub {\b Repository:} github.com/stephencummins/lemon_book {\b Page Layout:} 275 words per page average {\b Total Word Count:} Approximately 50,000 words {\b Page Count:} 186 pages\par}
